re are some but only if you choose to be a grumpy purist who refuses to get it through his head that literature and cinema are two very different media and therefore cannot be the same will never be the same.", :sentiment=>2, :context_tags=>{}, :emphasis=>1.0, :people_tags=>[], :people_indexes=>[]}, {:index=>22, :text=>"This is as great an adaptation as there will ever be.", :clean_text=>"this is as great an adaptation as there will ever be.", :sentiment=>2, :context_tags=>{}, :emphasis=>0.0, :people_tags=>[], :people_indexes=>[]}, {:index=>23, :text=>"Call me when you make a movie one-tenth this good.In my eyes, the films are in some ways better than the books.", :clean_text=>"call me when you make a movie one-tenth this good.in my eyes the films are in some ways better than the books.", :sentiment=>2, :context_tags=>{}, :emphasis=>0.0, :people_tags=>[], :people_indexes=>[]}, {:index=>24, :text=>"I find it extremely annoying that Tolkien's work is being idealized by his fans.", :clean_text=>"i find it extremely annoying that tolkien's work is being idealized by his fans.", :sentiment=>-2, :context_tags=>{}, :emphasis=>1.0, :people_tags=>[], :people_indexes=>[]}, {:index=>25, :text=>"He was but a man and he, too, made mistakes.", :clean_text=>"he was but a man and he too made mistakes.", :sentiment=>-2, :context_tags=>{}, :emphasis=>0.0, :people_tags=>[], :people_indexes=>[]}, {:index=>26, :text=>"His books, as detailed and amazing as they are, still aren't perfect.", :clean_text=>"his books as detailed and amazing as they are still aren't perfect.", :sentiment=>2, :context_tags=>{}, :emphasis=>0.0, :people_tags=>[], :people_indexes=>[]}, {:index=>27, :text=>"There are characters who do nothing but sit around, scenes the very presence of which is meaningless or at the very least questionable.", :clean_text=>"there are characters who do nothing but sit around scenes the very presence of which is meaningless or at the very least questionable.", :sentiment=>-2, :contex