r than the SE DVD, it is not the best this movie can look.", :clean_text=>"while it certainly looks better than the se dvd it is not the best this movie can look.", :sentiment=>2, :context_tags=>{}, :emphasis=>2.0, :people_tags=>[], :people_indexes=>[]}, {:index=>12, :text=>"The over-zealous Digital Noise Reduction that has been applied completely robs many scenes of the fine detail we might otherwise have seen in 1080p.", :clean_text=>"the over-zealous digital noise reduction that has been applied completely robs many scenes of the fine detail we might otherwise have seen in 1080p.", :sentiment=>-1, :context_tags=>{}, :emphasis=>1.0, :people_tags=>[], :people_indexes=>[]}, {:index=>13, :text=>"I put the old SE DVD in my Xbox and flipped back and forth between the Blu-Ray and DVD on a single scene (Blondie stands alone against some hills in the background in the final scene).", :clean_text=>"i put the old se dvd in my xbox and flipped back and forth between the blu-ray and dvd on a single scene blondie stands alone against some hills in the background in the final scene).", :sentiment=>0, :context_tags=>{:cinematography=>80}, :emphasis=>3.0, :people_tags=>[], :people_indexes=>[]}, {:index=>14, :text=>"While the Blu-Ray looked \"cleaner\" (that is, the digital artifacting visible on the DVD was gone), there was actually no further detail to be seen on the Blu-Ray!", :clean_text=>"while the blu-ray looked cleaner that is the digital artifacting visible on the dvd was gone there was actually no further detail to be seen on the blu-ray!", :sentiment=>0, :context_tags=>{}, :emphasis=>2.0, :people_tags=>[], :people_indexes=>[]}, {:index=>15, :text=>"It was as if you took the DVD image and smeared it until the noise was gone, then bumped it up to 1080.", :clean_text=>"it was as if you took the dvd image and smeared it until the noise was gone then bumped it up to 1080.", :sentiment=>0, :context_tags=>{:cinematography=>20}, :emphasis=>1.0, :people_tags=>[], :people_indexes=