.", :clean_text=>"it starts slowly as a band of bounty killers home in on their prey small-time bandit tuco ramirez the ugly played by the venerable eli wallach).", :sentiment=>-1, :context_tags=>{:cast=>70}, :emphasis=>2.0, :people_tags=>["Eli Wallach"], :people_indexes=>[["Eli Wallach", [[136]]]]}, {:index=>16, :text=>"They pile through a saloon door, then the camera imediately pans away laterally.", :clean_text=>"they pile through a saloon door then the camera imediately pans away laterally.", :sentiment=>0, :context_tags=>{}, :emphasis=>0.0, :people_tags=>[], :people_indexes=>[]}, {:index=>17, :text=>"Suddenly, his body hurtling through the front window in a rain of glass, Tuco bursts onto the street -- in what has to be the most absurd grand entrance in screen history -- revolver in one hand, a chicken leg in the other.", :clean_text=>"suddenly his body hurtling through the front window in a rain of glass tuco bursts onto the street in what has to be the most absurd grand entrance in screen history revolver in one hand a chicken leg in the other.", :sentiment=>0, :context_tags=>{:vision=>70}, :emphasis=>0.0, :people_tags=>["Eli Wallach"], :people_indexes=>[]}, {:index=>18, :text=>"It's total chutzpah on Leone's and Wallach's part.If you think *that* can't be topped, watch Wallach's entire performance.", :clean_text=>"it's total chutzpah on leone's and wallach's part.if you think that can't be topped watch wallach's entire performance.", :sentiment=>0, :context_tags=>{:cast=>90}, :emphasis=>1.0, :people_tags=>[], :people_indexes=>[]}, {:index=>19, :text=>"Animated is putting it mildly.", :clean_text=>"animated is putting it mildly.", :sentiment=>1, :context_tags=>{}, :emphasis=>0.0, :people_tags=>[], :people_indexes=>[]}, {:index=>20, :text=>"More than a performance, Wallach is a one-man band, nay, Army.", :clean_text=>"more than a performance wallach is a one-man band nay army.", :sentiment=>0, :context_tags=>{:cast=>90}, :emphasis=>0.0, :people_tags=>[], :peop