 :content=>"\n\nThis film probably had the largest impact on my life. It set the tone for\neverything I then got interested in. American Civil War. Film Music. Clint\nEastwood. Real Westerns. This is the best of the Dollars Trilogy and by far\none of the best Westerns of all time. It has drama, comedy, cracking\ndialogue, some of the most brutal battle scenes - especially around the\nbridge - that I'd seen up to then, music to die for and set pieces that just\nooze atmosphere and tension. I have never forgotten the end shoot-out. This\nwas unique; 3 people?! You can't do that. But Leone did, and he did it\nbrilliantly - all cameras and music. I have now seen this film too many\ntimes to count but I'll be back for another blast of buono, brutto, cattivo,\nsomeday. My son owes his name to this film. Yep, that there is Clinton.\n\n", :source=>{:vendor=>"imdb", :url=>"http://www.imdb.com/title/tt0060196/"}, :rescore_review=>[{:index=>0, :text=>"\n\nThis film probably had the largest impact on my life.", :clean_text=>"this film probably had the largest impact on my life.", :sentiment=>0, :context_tags=>{}, :emphasis=>0.0, :people_tags=>[], :people_indexes=>[]}, {:index=>1, :text=>"It set the tone for\neverything I then got interested in. American Civil War.", :clean_text=>"it set the tone for everything i then got interested in american civil war.", :sentiment=>1, :context_tags=>{}, :emphasis=>1.0, :people_tags=>[], :people_indexes=>[]}, {:index=>2, :text=>"Film Music.", :clean_text=>"film music.", :sentiment=>0, :context_tags=>{:sound=>100}, :emphasis=>0.0, :people_tags=>[], :people_indexes=>[]}, {:index=>3, :text=>"Clint\nEastwood.", :clean_text=>"clint eastwood.", :sentiment=>0, :context_tags=>{}, :emphasis=>0.0, :people_tags=>[], :people_indexes=>[]}, {:index=>4, :text=>"Real Westerns.", :clean_text=>"real westerns.", :sentiment=>1, :context_tags=>{}, :emphasis=>0.0, :people_tags=>[], :people_indexes=>[]}, {:index=>5, :text=>"This is the best of the Dollars Trilogy a