need to reveal the way they got to the top and how now they're going to take over the world, blah, blah, blah and the hero, being, of course, smarter and wiser, kills him while he talks. An even better thing about this film is that everyone here is a bad guy and we see none of those repertories before a guy is going to shoot someone, thank you very much. Not only that but I also learned that there's always two kinds of people in this world, my friend...", :title=>nil, :location=>nil, :source=>{:vendor=>"rotten_tomatoes", :url=>"http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/the_good_the_bad_and_the_ugly"}, :rescore_review=>[{:index=>0, :text=>"Classic western film.", :clean_text=>"classic western film.", :sentiment=>1, :context_tags=>{}, :emphasis=>0.0, :people_tags=>[], :people_indexes=>[]}, {:index=>1, :text=>"Loved it!", :clean_text=>"loved it!", :sentiment=>0, :context_tags=>{}, :emphasis=>1.0, :people_tags=>[], :people_indexes=>[]}, {:index=>2, :text=>"\"If you're gonna shoot, don't talk, shoot.", :clean_text=>"\"if you're gonna shoot don't talk shoot.", :sentiment=>0, :context_tags=>{}, :emphasis=>0.0, :people_tags=>[], :people_indexes=>[]}, {:index=>3, :text=>"\"Well I obviously watched the director's cut (I didn't realize this until I heard a bit of the commentary... I actually thought the film had been THAT long) and though I think I should've watched the \"normal version\" first, I absolutely loved this movie.", :clean_text=>"\"well i obviously watched the director's cut i didn't realize this until i heard a bit of the commentary i actually thought the film had been that long and though i think i should've watched the normal version first i absolutely loved this movie.", :sentiment=>-2, :context_tags=>{:length=>50}, :emphasis=>1.0, :people_tags=>[], :people_indexes=>[]}, {:index=>4, :text=>"Why?", :clean_text=>"why?", :sentiment=>0, :context_tags=>{}, :emphasis=>1.0, :people_tags=>[], :people_indexes=>[]}, {:index=>5, :text=>"Well first off, there's Clint Eastwood (the G