nce from Meatloaf as well? Who knew?!?! Aside from the main cast and one or two of the side characters, no one else is really that developed and the movie plays out more like a fantasy than actual events, which contradicts the realistic tone it sets. Breaking the 4th wall is something I love to see in movies and is extremely rare to see in anything that isn't a comedy. Overall: Fight Club is an utterly brilliant movie that is almost perfect. A few minor flaws here and there, but nothing that really ruins it. A must see.", :useful=>[3.0, 3], :username=>"Rox22", :date=>"Mar 27, 2013", :location=>nil, :title=>nil, :source=>{:vendor=>"metacritic", :url=>"http://www.metacritic.com/movie/fight-club"}, :rescore_review=>[{:index=>0, :text=>"A pretty fine movie that was brilliant in its day. Still is to a lesser extent. Fight Club was clever and well written with fantastic performances from Norton And Pitt. Oddly a rather decent performance from Meatloaf as well?", :clean_text=>"a pretty fine movie that was brilliant in its day still is to a lesser extent fight club was clever and well written with fantastic performances from norton and pitt oddly a rather decent performance from meatloaf as well?", :sentiment=>2, :context_tags=>{:cast=>90}, :emphasis=>1.0, :people_tags=>[], :people_indexes=>[]}, {:index=>1, :text=>"Who knew?!?!", :clean_text=>"who knew?!?!", :sentiment=>0, :context_tags=>{}, :emphasis=>3.0, :people_tags=>[], :people_indexes=>[]}, {:index=>2, :text=>"Aside from the main cast and one or two of the side characters, no one else is really that developed and the movie plays out more like a fantasy thanA pretty fine movie that was brilliant in its day. Still is to a lesser extent. Fight Club was clever and well written with fantastic performances from Norton And Pitt. Oddly a rather decent performance from Meatloaf as well?", :clean_text=>"aside from the main cast and one or two of the side characters no one else is really that developed and the movie plays out mo