e high definition transfer and the lossless audio (DTS-HD Master Audio 5.1) restoration of the film from the 35mm film original negative. Special features include:Voices from the List: Documentary featuring a number of testimonies and stories from men and women who survived the Holocaust thanks to Oskar Schindler.USC Shoah Foundation Story with Steven Spielberg", :rating=>5.0, :percentage=>100.0, :useful=>[96, 105], :date=>" 2013 January 23", :title=>"A masterpiece for all time", :location=>"(Fort Worth, TX USA)", :username=>"M. Oleson", :source=>{:vendor=>"amazon", :url=>"http://www.amazon.com/Schindlers-List-Blu-ray-DIGITAL-UltraViolet/product-reviews/B00B0U2SEA"}, :rescore_review=>[{:index=>0, :text=>"Steven Spielberg finally got the long awaited respect he deserved as director when he won the Oscar for his 3 hour 16 minute epic.", :clean_text=>"steven spielberg finally got the long awaited respect he deserved as director when he won the oscar for his 3 hour 16 minute epic.", :sentiment=>2, :context_tags=>{:length=>50}, :emphasis=>0.0, :people_tags=>["Steven Spielberg"], :people_indexes=>[]}, {:index=>1, :text=>"And now this excellent 20th Anniversary Blu ray finally arrives.", :clean_text=>"and now this excellent 20th anniversary blu ray finally arrives.", :sentiment=>2, :context_tags=>{}, :emphasis=>0.0, :people_tags=>[], :people_indexes=>[]}, {:index=>2, :text=>"Spielberg shot in black and white because he says that is how he pictures all the events in his mind.", :clean_text=>"spielberg shot in black and white because he says that is how he pictures all the events in his mind.", :sentiment=>-1, :context_tags=>{:cinematography=>80}, :emphasis=>0.0, :people_tags=>[], :people_indexes=>[]}, {:index=>3, :text=>"As a kid he had seen some photos and they were B & W.  With a splash of color at the beginning and end, he also tosses in an effective shot of a little girl walking through chaos wearing a red coat.Brilliant movie making but certainly not a movie that can b